{
  "texts": [
    "49, KL-annealing has the potential to increase reconstruction ability for VAE.",
    "By applying KL-annealing we expect to increase the efficiency of KL-PMVAE in information extraction.",
    "The survival outcomes of different predicted risk groups were presented using Kaplan-Meier (KM) curves.",
    "Cox proportional hazard (CoxPH) models were also used to study the association between the survival outcome and one or more variables.",
    "We used R (survival 62, survminer 63) and Python (lifelines 64) packages to implement the survival analysis approaches."
  ]
}